snippet.title: Domiverse - How to play - Snakity
snippet.description:
How to play Snakity

The Snakats wants to win the Domiverse to mark territory on all the planets of the universe!
Snakity can combo with a jumping attack, an air flip, a dive attack or even a slide attack. Be careful of the power of love!

http://domiverse.be

Steam store: http://store.steampowered.com/app/598880/Domiverse/
